{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"getter"},{"kind":"text","text":"="},{"kind":"identifier","text":"isDraggable"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"draggable"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If this property is set to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":", the user can drag the annotation after","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"pressing and holding the view, and the associated annotation object must also","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"implement the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setCoordinate:"},{"text":" method. The default value of this property is","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Setting this property to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":" lets the map view know that the annotation is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"always draggable. In other words, you cannot conditionalize drag operations by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"attempting to stop an operation that has already been initiated; doing so can"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"lead to undefined behavior. Once begun, the drag operation should always"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"continue to completion."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":4,"anchor":"Related-examples","text":"Related examples","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Enable users to drag ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" objects on your map.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/draggable","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","title":"draggable","roleHeading":"Instance Property","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L261","fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h"},"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)draggable","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"draggable","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"draggable","kind":"identifier"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the annotation view is draggable."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/draggable"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/draggable":{"title":"draggable","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/draggable","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/draggable","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"draggable"}],"abstract":[{"text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the annotation view is draggable.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"title":"MLNAnnotationView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}]}}}